  <p>The Wuji Labs journal publishes new essays in English and Chinese, roughly every couple of weeks. Pick a language tag at signup — <em>EN</em>, <em>ZH</em>, or <em>both</em> — and the sends are segmented accordingly. No cross-language spam.</p>
  <p>The full subscribe surface (Buttondown form, language-tag selector, DKIM/SPF-authenticated sends) lands in Phase 5 of the site reorg. For now, watch <a href="https://github.com/WujiLabs">github.com/WujiLabs</a> for the journal launch.</p>
